<title>USA: Continental promotes Bethune to chairman.</title>
<headline>Continental promotes Bethune to chairman.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1996-10-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Continental Airlines Inc said Tuesday it had named Chief Executive Officer Gordon Bethune as chairman, succeeding David Bonderman.</p>
<p>Bonderman, whose Air Partners investment group is Continental's largest shareholder, remains chairman of the executive committee and a member of the board, the airline said.</p>
<p>Chief Operating Officer Gregory Brenneman has succeeded Bethune as president, Continental said.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
